==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Flaxen
<hw>Flax"en</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Made of flax;
resembling flax or its fibers; of the color of flax; of a light soft
straw color; fair and flowing, like flax or tow; <as>as, <ex>flaxen</ex>
thread; <ex>flaxen</ex> hair.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flax-plant</ent>⟦br⟧
